                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for efficiently utilizing vanadium titano-magnetite at low carbon",
                    "一种低碳高效利用钒钛磁铁矿的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for efficiently utilizing vanadium titano-magnetite at low carbon, which comprises the following steps of: mixing vanadium titano-magnetite concentrate with dust and sludge at the top of a hydrogen-based shaft furnace to prepare pellets by adopting a belt type machine roasting-hydrogen-based shaft furnace pre-reduction-electric furnace melting separation process, oxidizing and roasting the pellets by utilizing a belt type machine, and canceling the cooling process of the traditional pellets; the pellets are charged into a hydrogen-based shaft furnace in a high-temperature hot mode, and rapid reduction is conducted through introduced hydrogen or hydrogen-rich gas and the high temperature of the pellets; and then the obtained pre-reduced pellets are thermally charged into an electric furnace, low-carbon-emission fuel and a reducing agent are adopted, the repeated heating-cooling link in the metallurgical process is reduced, carbon emission in the vanadium titano-magnetite smelting process is greatly reduced, and low-carbon and efficient utilization of iron, vanadium, titanium and other elements in the vanadium titano-magnetite is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种低碳高效利用钒钛磁铁矿的方法，采用带式机焙烧‑氢基竖炉预还原‑电炉熔分的工艺，先将钒钛磁铁精矿与氢基竖炉炉顶尘泥混合配料，制备成球团，并利用带式机进行球团的氧化焙烧，取消传统球团的冷却过程，高温热装入氢基竖炉，利用通入的氢气或富氢气体和球团自身高温快速还原；之后将得到的预还原球团热装入电炉内，并采用低碳排放的燃料和还原剂，减少冶金过程中反复加热‑冷却环节，大幅降低钒钛磁铁矿冶炼过程中的碳排放，实现低碳、高效利用钒钛磁铁矿中铁、钒、钛等元素。"
                }
            ]
